  ğŸš€ What is System Design?   

    " Designing how a big software system works internally so it can handle millions of users smoothly."
  
            It means deciding:

              -> How data flows
              -> How fast the system should be
              -> How to handle more users
              -> How to store, fetch, and secure data
              -> How different parts talk to each other

